    <item>
      <title>华尔街前所未有地展现激进投资者的力量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-06/wall-street-flexes-activist-muscles-like-never-before-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱全球股东咨询主管 Jim Rossman 在“彭博未平仓头寸”节目中表示，尽管美国激进投资者在全球激进投资者中所占比例有所下降，但 2024 年激进投资者罢免首席执行官的人数比以往任何时候都多。他表示，越来越多的投资者选择激进主义来推动变革。Sonali Basak 的华尔街快讯将于周五发布。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-06/wall-street-flexes-activist-muscles-like-never-before-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 15:30:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>库克称美联储官员降息可更加谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-06/fed-officials-can-be-more-cautions-with-cuts-cook-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事丽莎·库克表示，决策者“可以更加谨慎地进一步降息”，理由是劳动力市场强劲，近期通胀数据波动较大。库克周一在密歇根州安娜堡举行的第七届法律与宏观经济学会议上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-06/fed-officials-can-be-more-cautions-with-cuts-cook-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 15:29:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储库克称官员们在降息方面可以更加谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/fed-s-cook-says-officials-can-be-more-cautious-with-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事丽莎·库克表示，由于劳动力市场强劲且通胀压力持续存在，政策制定者可以更加谨慎地采取降息措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/fed-s-cook-says-officials-can-be-more-cautious-with-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 14:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>因担心科特迪瓦出口放缓将导致供应紧张，可可价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/cocoa-gains-on-fears-slowing-ivorian-exports-will-tighten-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们越来越担心主要生产国科特迪瓦的供应减少将进一步挤压本已紧张的市场，纽约可可价格创下一周多以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/cocoa-gains-on-fears-slowing-ivorian-exports-will-tighten-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 13:45:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
